        ## ðŸ’» Features
        
        - Minimal low-level Python client that allows you to interact with Cord's API
        - Supports Python: `3.6`, `3.7`, and `3.8`
        
        ## âœ¨ Relevant Links
        * [Cord website](https://cord.tech)
